ver had in a hotel, with a tub big enough for the two of us to sit down and stretch out completely. The view wasn't much, but had we been on the other side, there are great views to be had. There was even a little shopping boulevard on the way to the tower area from the casino floor. The vendors there weren't very pushy and very polite. This room made our trip so perfect we were ready to stay another night.The thing that brought everything together was the customer service at the Tropicana. People there were more than willing to help make up for the mistakes beyond their control. Service was friendly and always prompt. I would definitely stay there again, but this time I'll get the Island Tower to start!	
