rived there I ended getting to the lobby thru the back of the hotel by the Garden Rooms and my very first encounter was that of a hooker tyring to find a room! I saw a guy calling to her from his balcony and later saw the same guy wandering the halls looking for her. Lovely! Oh well, you get what you pay for! Next time I'll stay at the Mandalay Bay if a pool is what I am after.	
